item.title: book babes HOP
item.description: (transcribed from Book Six 3:17pm JST Sunday 28 June 2009 (day 14340)) 4:30AM Sunday 5 December 1993 [page 44] I am tired. I read Illusions by Richard Bach today, the day of Lori's going away party which I didn't attend because Nathan was going to be there. I determined that I am intimidated by Lori and other females in their (Lori & Suzanne's) group. My upper left jaw is fucked up.
